T1  - Expatriates ill after travel: results from the Geosentinel Surveillance Network.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1186/1471-2334-12-386
A1  - Lim, Poh-Lian
A1  - Han, Pauline
A1  - Chen, Lin H
A1  - MacDonald, Susan
A1  - Pandey, Prativa
A1  - Hale, DeVon
