T1  - Spectrum of imported infectious diseases among children and adolescents returning from the tropics and subtropics.
T3  - Comment in: J Travel Med. 2012 May-Jun;19(3):137-9. doi: 10.1111/j.1708-8305.2012.00598.x PMID: 22530818 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22530818]
