T1  - Assessment of prenatal mercury exposure in a predominately Caribbean immigrant community in Brooklyn, NY.
T3  - Comment in: J Environ Monit. 2012 Oct 26;14(10):2815-6; discussion 217-8. doi: 10.1039/c2em30475a PMID: 22951974 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22951974]
