T1  - Post-earthquake outbreak of insecticide-associated conjunctivitis in a primary school of Lixian district, China: An epidemiological investigation.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.puhe.2010.02.017
A1  - Xiong, H Y
