T1  - Mental health problems among adults in tsunami-affected areas in southern Thailand.
T3  - Comment in: JAMA. 2006 Aug 2;296(5):576-8. doi: 10.1001/jama.296.5.576 PMID: 16882965 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16882965] Comment in: Evid Based Ment Health. 2007 Feb;10(1):31. doi: 10.1136/ebmh.10.1.31 PMID: 17255400 [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17255400]
